    <item>
      <title>日本央行维持利率不变，日元兑美元跌破 155 关键水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行维持利率不变后，日元兑美元汇率跌破155的关键水平。日本股票和债券期货继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Taw 表示，“美国例外主义”将在 2025 年继续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/timothy-taw-on-the-china-show-12-19-asia-markets-wrap-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德的托马斯·托表示，“美国例外论”预计明年将继续，但投资者正在关注美国股市的驱动因素。托在彭博电视台讨论了他对 2025 年的展望。

（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/timothy-taw-on-the-china-show-12-19-asia-markets-wrap-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:42:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电池制造商 CATL 考虑在香港上市，募资 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，宁德时代科技股份有限公司正考虑在香港进行第二次上市，可能募集至少 50 亿美元资金，这将是自 2021 年初以来香港规模最大的一次上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后华尔街交易员纷纷退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在引发金融市场大幅上涨近一年后，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周三却做出了完全相反的举动，对 2025 年的降息持谨慎态度，令投资者感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
